{"tid":1362868,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［遍地開花］機管局員工有野講","createTime":"2019-07-25T03:59:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T09:20:01.000Z","uid":285839,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7dd3e072e1ef9f2b611c3d2f873e204ddaf3ba6b","tid":1362868,"uid":285839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:59:37.000Z","msg":"致香港市民<br />\n<br />\n我們是一群機管局及機場員工。<br />\n<br />\n於7月21號晚上於元朗西鐵站發生的恐怖襲擊事件中，警方刻意延遲到達現場，導致無辜市民不斷被追打，陷入一片恐慌，求救無門。市民亦能從多個媒體片段中看到多名警員明目張膽與手持武器的白衣懷疑施暴者交談後，拍拍背脊便讓白衣人離開。我們對警察此等行為感到極度憤怒！<br />\n<br />\n警隊多次暴力對待、圍捕示威者，721晚上於上環一帶，肆意濫用布袋彈、橡膠子彈、催淚氣體！無警示情況下水平線連開36槍，更於天橋位置從上而下把示威者當成活把，任意射殺！<br />\n<br />\n自6月9日以來，香港市民嘅抗爭已經過45天，經歷過二百萬人和平示威，散落各區的光復遊行，政府不但對市民5大訴求無動於衷，更不斷用言語偽術，企圖轉移視線。 我們認為單單撤回送中條例及成立獨立調查委員會，已經不能夠有效解決現時社會矛盾，必須確切落實真．雙普選才能夠建立出一個真正屬於人民嘅政府！<br />\n<br />\n我哋重申：<br />\n政府必須立即落實五大訴求, 缺一不可<br />\n1 撤回逃犯條例修定<br />\n2 撤回任何暴動定性<br />\n3 撤銷所有抗爭者控罪<br />\n4 成立獨立調查委員會 追究警隊濫權濫暴<br />\n5 立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n726 機場見 <br />\n<br />\n一班熱愛香港嘅機管局及機場員工上<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後記<br />\n員工心聲 1：<br />\n我是在機場管理局工作，由元朗黑社會暴力事件開始，除了在午飯時間大家會在討論事件之外，好像沒有一個會主動提出為香港人做些什麼，大家其實都好憤怒，不過可以做的就只有看Facebook /YouTube 去跟進事情的發展，見到CX 發起集會，在機管局內，好像還沒有一個人表示支持，又眼見好多政府部門/私人機構的職員都放上自己的職員証表達意見，可是機管局的職員証就一個也沒有（希望只是我看不到）我就做第一個人<br />\n <br />\n員工心聲 2：<br />\n作為香港人, 社會去到今時今日咁樣嘅情況, 仲邊有可能唔行出嚟講, 黑官黑鄉黑警!<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/25/115510_645f6357ece11f3ccba6de99ed1c6d31.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F25%2F115510_645f6357ece11f3ccba6de99ed1c6d31.png&h=c18eead5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/25/115514_c968936a9dba4d6d064d6a95d4cc090a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F25%2F115514_c968936a9dba4d6d064d6a95d4cc090a.png&h=562a4963&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/25/115518_7d86f9375e7ff8e74a282f3099252dad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F25%2F115518_7d86f9375e7ff8e74a282f3099252dad.png&h=cd3dea7b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/25/115520_b4e4c5b1fd3ae679156390b8198614ce.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F25%2F115520_b4e4c5b1fd3ae679156390b8198614ce.png&h=34c47141&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/25/115522_39209cbdd768d57da482a659ac4aa84e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F25%2F115522_39209cbdd768d57da482a659ac4aa84e.png&h=10c0d28a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/25/115524_b5d3d93c5f4fdfaebd9b37afb7d55c66.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F25%2F115524_b5d3d93c5f4fdfaebd9b37afb7d55c66.png&h=00728016&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/25/115530_5970fd3129678f9370c97db3fb627156.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F25%2F115530_5970fd3129678f9370c97db3fb627156.png&h=d7404a12&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3584ebfdb141091ddf7fdf1f68cd6e4ebf282871","tid":1362868,"uid":285839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:07:39.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"1a92a01321dda63622aba28faad544684ab3d82e","tid":1362868,"uid":285839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:10:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e486b5667dabcd9725d779bd6cf117fa1f76d00","tid":1362868,"uid":165683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:14:54.000Z","msg":"726見"},{"pid":"42e3311350c95ca6e629d02086eb853d4a4b9ef3","tid":1362868,"uid":267189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:15:57.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲<br />\n小弟見到好多遍地開花嘅post，好感動<br />\n不同行業嘅巴絲都出嚟發聲<br />\n<br />\n但係因為連登啲post好散同埋facebook接觸到嘅年齡層面相對連登會更加廣<br />\n所以開一個facebook page去整合一啲政府部門同公營機構嘅遍地開花post裡面嘅相<br />\n<br />\n點解淨係整政府部門同公營機構呢？<br />\n因為佢哋發聲嘅震撼力比較大同埋小弟能力有限，未能夠整合晒各行各業嘅post<br />\n<br />\n如果有巴絲其實只係想post喺連登，而唔想擺喺facebook，歡迎pm我，我會即刻delete返<br />\n<br />\n而如果有喺政府部門或者公營機構工作嘅巴絲想post去facebook，歡迎喺facebook pm呢個page: <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/civilservantsflowers/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcivilservantsflowers%2F&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07D8mKZra6PqY6jPBlhHcv87Y%3D&h=26740bc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/civilservantsflowers/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各有各做"},{"pid":"c54e27c383aa7882726f353026ae8bc4e85e4ecb","tid":1362868,"uid":50737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:16:26.000Z","msg":"多謝你地"},{"pid":"b6d6393ab44abd8202dd78542c631ed785a6ecff","tid":1362868,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:16:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a99f641ee36d44de95a5b7757569f35b29dd4e43","tid":1362868,"uid":254729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:18:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e01b3ec21cc0f4174e9724f09152aebbdd2e8f06","tid":1362868,"uid":57728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:44:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0b1ec1d4ecb8ee3cb764900d0a6e5d3f8069060b","tid":1362868,"uid":236847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T05:51:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35f03d6dabf0c6add061affe3080ad159df7305e","tid":1362868,"uid":61451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:32:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d64588e333bfce03efc54e0a0d22b8526a